data.description: Welcome to this beautiful two story home located in Kingdom Heights. Upon entering is the spacious open-concept living area with luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout. The kitchen boasts an island with seating space, stainless steel appliances, white cabinetry, contemporary finishes & a walk-in pantry. The primary suite is on the 1st floor & offers a soaking tub, separate shower, dual-sink vanity & walk-in closet. Upstairs you will find the large gameroom & secondary bedrooms. Covered patio with ceiling fan overlooks the large private backyard that has no back neighbors. Walking/biking distance to the community pool, rec center & playground. The community has acres of parks & lakes, and it is conveniently located with easy access to 59, 90 & Westpark. Zoned to sought-after Lamar Consolidated schools. Don't miss this one!
